	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YXRpb249Ijc4MDAwMCIgLz4NCiAgICAgIDx3b3JrSXRlbSBmcm9tPSIxNjg3MDI5NDMxMDc4IiBkdXJhdGlvbj0iNDA2MDAwIiAvPg0KICAgICAgPHdvcmtJdGVtIGZyb209IjE2ODcwODk3MDk3MDgiIGR1cmF0aW9uPSI1MjE0MDAwIiAvPg0KICAgIDwvdGFzaz4N'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('CiAgICA8c2VydmVycyAvPg0KICA8L2NvbXBvbmVudD4NCiAgPGNvbXBvbmVudCBuYW1lPSJUeXBlU2NyaXB0R2VuZXJhdGVkRmlsZXNNYW5hZ2VyIj4NCiAgICA8b3B0aW9uIG5hbWU9InZlcnNpb24iIHZhbHVlPSIzIiAvPg0KICA8L2NvbXBvbmVudD4NCiAgPGNv'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bXBvbmVudCBuYW1lPSJYU0xULVN1cHBvcnQuRmlsZUFzc29jaWF0aW9ucy5VSVN0YXRlIj4NCiAgICA8ZXhwYW5kIC8+DQogICAgPHNlbGVjdCAvPg0KICA8L2NvbXBvbmVudD4NCjwvcHJvamVjdD4='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .idea/workspace.xml');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') != '7fc15e26d149da0560027d83eab2e58a2339b1fe') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/workspace.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/workspace.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '7fc15e26d149da0560027d83eab2e58a2339b1fe') {
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '6aadc041e80d3002503951500b7dff6f1fdb9260') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/workspace.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/workspace.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/workspace.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/workspace.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '7fc15e26d149da0560027d83eab2e58a2339b1fe') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/config_values.md');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') != '17b90497002a5b973d71dc9319ea06727c1db92b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/config_values.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/config_values.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '17b90497002a5b973d71dc9319ea06727c1db92b') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '365ace3f029a281885254052bf75ba8f25317bb5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/config_values.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/config_values.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/config_values.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/config_values.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '17b90497002a5b973d71dc9319ea06727c1db92b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
		}
	}
}

	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') != '35dbc8e2c76a98c371fc7423e40815f59643c947') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== '35dbc8e2c76a98c371fc7423e40815f59643c947') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== 'ef6f4d44e6c2026ae1071a00fec742806f9099c4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== '35dbc8e2c76a98c371fc7423e40815f59643c947') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != 'f9835e636dcdfbe12046224111973a79f54f0b4d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'f9835e636dcdfbe12046224111973a79f54f0b4d') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'cc067ca532a03066c3fa7c4aaf92fc2a0ed1d58f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'f9835e636dcdfbe12046224111973a79f54f0b4d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') != '0bcc51d342c98678d57415a7569b0d8926dc539e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '0bcc51d342c98678d57415a7569b0d8926dc539e') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '219bf3039903cabd56bb064a656f91d921d14730') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '0bcc51d342c98678d57415a7569b0d8926dc539e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/910_automated_ajax_calls/OIDplusPageAdminAutomatedAJAXCalls.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/910_automated_ajax_calls/OIDplusPageAdminAutomatedAJAXCalls.class.php') !== 'a2a7877559dec89c762b2ed3e53b0a5548913d55') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/910_automated_ajax_calls/OIDplusPageAdminAutomatedAJAXCalls.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '8497ac10228e18db1599e604d1ead39d8859a061') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '8497ac10228e18db1599e604d1ead39d8859a061') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '1296bb38f5b721c63f060c3d426fbe7206f31bca') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '8497ac10228e18db1599e604d1ead39d8859a061') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php') != 'b0452f050efe979240c7166ff9df07d7592f6b2b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php') !== 'b0452f050efe979240c7166ff9df07d7592f6b2b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php') !== '65aed98d816c40a35862b78dbb3e42f5ef36f748') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php') !== 'b0452f050efe979240c7166ff9df07d7592f6b2b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	writefile_22();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') != '28111f6ab8965e5b859a8ff9986c0c8f606910a6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '28111f6ab8965e5b859a8ff9986c0c8f606910a6') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '5d93d5781f64786aeb352fd8717f1e05e0f9bed6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_22();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '28111f6ab8965e5b859a8ff9986c0c8f606910a6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != 'e13c750456ae9951b386603f27ad5ca9ee7f0d5e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'e13c750456ae9951b386603f27ad5ca9ee7f0d5e') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'ff3c7062d5aa49e0e27cbe343537dd353d7b2c72') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'e13c750456ae9951b386603f27ad5ca9ee7f0d5e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}
}
